BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 11 Tf 50 656 Td (Pass your key in the HTTP request header. This keeps it out of browser history,) Tj ET
BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 11 Tf 50 639 Td (server logs, and URLs. This is the industry-standard practice.) Tj ET
0.94 0.96 0.99 rg 50 600 495 32 re f
