0.10 0.65 0.38 rg 50 455 495 26 re f
BT 1.00 1.00 1.00 rg /F2 13 Tf 57 466 Td (Security Best Practices) Tj ET
BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 10 Tf 63 435 Td (  -  Store your API key in environment variables, never in source code.) Tj ET
BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 10 Tf 63 417 Td (  -  Rotate your key immediately via the bot if you suspect it is compromised.) Tj ET
BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 10 Tf 63 399 Td (  -  Use the Authorization header in all server-to-server or production calls.) Tj ET
BT 0.07 0.18 0.28 rg /F1 10 Tf 63 381 Td (  -  Rate limit applies per key: 30 requests per minute. Cache responses when possible.) Tj ET
